# Test Sync Endpoint
# Use this to manually test if the sync is working

### 1. Test manual sync for employee 1
POST http://192.168.3.39:3000/api/hr/employees/1/sync-balances
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_HR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Test leave approval (replace :id with actual leave request ID)
PUT http://192.168.3.39:3000/api/hr/leave-requests/21/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_HR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

### 3. Test leave rejection
PUT http://192.168.3.39:3000/api/hr/leave-requests/21/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_HR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "REJECTED",
  "rejection_reason": "Testing rejection"
}

### 4. Check employee balances
GET http://192.168.3.39:3000/api/hr/employees/1/balances
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_HR_TOKEN_HERE
